        "ERC20Airdrop2: claimedAmount, withdrawnAmount, withdrawalWindow",
        "EssentialContract: paused status, reentrancy lock (transient or storage), AddressResolver state (via inheritance; addressManager pointer not shown here)",
        "SigVerifyLib: ES256VERIFIER address"
      ],
      "privilege_assets": [
        "Owner privileges across UUPS-upgradeable contracts inheriting EssentialContract (upgrade authority via _authorizeUpgrade onlyOwner)",
        "Pause/unpause authority in EssentialContract (gated by _authorizePause onlyOwner by default, but pause/unpause are public entry points)",
        "AddressResolver-based named roles (onlyFromNamed / onlyFromOwnerOrNamed) e.g., TaikoL2.withdraw uses named role 'withdrawer'; CrossChainOwned.onMessageInvocation requires named 'bridge'",
        "AutomataDcapV3Attestation owner: can change trust lists, revocation lists, TCB/QE identity configuration, and toggle local report checks",
        "TaikoL2 GOLDEN_TOUCH_ADDRESS privilege: sole caller of anchor()"
      ],
      "reputation_assets": [
        "SGX/DCAP attestation trust configuration (tcbInfo, qeIdentity, revocation lists) impacts protocol proof acceptance",
        "Merkle airdrop claim integrity (merkleRoot and isClaimed) impacts airdrop fairness and user trust",
        "Cross-chain ownership security (ownerChainId/nextTxId sequencing + bridge context checks) impacts governance/administration credibility",
        "EIP-1559 basefee correctness on L2 (gasExcess/publicInputHash anchoring) impacts network economics and user trust"
      ]
