      "inheritance_hierarchy": "EssentialContract (UUPSUpgradeable + Ownable2StepUpgradeable + AddressResolver) is the core base for upgradeable admin/pausing/reentrancy and name-based access. CrossChainOwned inherits EssentialContract and implements IMessageInvocable for bridge-driven admin calls with src-chain ownership checks. TaikoL2 inherits CrossChainOwned and adds anchoring/basefee logic and withdrawals. TaikoL2EIP1559Configurable inherits TaikoL2 and exposes config setter. MerkleClaimable inherits EssentialContract and provides merkle claim gating; ERC20Airdrop/ERC20Airdrop2/ERC721Airdrop inherit MerkleClaimable. TimelockTokenPool inherits EssentialContract. AutomataDcapV3Attestation is a standalone non-upgradeable Ownable-like contract (custom owner variable) implementing IAttestation; it uses V3Parser/PEMCertChainLib/ISigVerifyLib. SigVerifyLib is a standalone non-upgradeable contract implementing ISigVerifyLib.",
      "external_dependencies": [
        "OpenZeppelin: IERC20, SafeERC20, IERC721, MerkleProof, ECDSA, IVotes, UUPSUpgradeable, Ownable2StepUpgradeable",
        "Solady: Base64, LibString",
        "Solmate: LibFixedPointMath",
        "nomad-xyz: ExcessivelySafeCall",
        "EVM precompile address(5) modexp via RsaVerify",
        "External ES256 verifier contract (address set in SigVerifyLib constructor)",
        "External AddressManager/AddressResolver (not included in snippet) used for resolve(name,...) checks",
        "External SignalService (ISignalService) resolved by name 'signal_service'",
        "External Bridge (IBridge) resolved by name 'bridge'"
      ],
      "upgrade_patterns": "UUPS proxy pattern for contracts inheriting EssentialContract (UUPSUpgradeable). Non-upgradeable standalone contracts: AutomataDcapV3Attestation, SigVerifyLib, PEMCertChainLib (deployed as a contract but no proxy pattern indicated). No Diamond pattern detected.",
      "access_control_structure": "Owner-centric control via Ownable2StepUpgradeable (EssentialContract) plus AddressResolver-based named roles (onlyFromNamed, onlyFromOwnerOrNamed). Pause/unpause are public but gated by _authorizePause (onlyOwner by default). CrossChainOwned enables cross-chain owner execution through Bridge.onMessageInvocation with strict context checks (srcChainId == ownerChainId and ctx.from == owner()). AutomataDcapV3Attestation uses a custom owner variable and onlyOwner modifier. TaikoL2.anchor is gated to a fixed GOLDEN_TOUCH_ADDRESS. Reentrancy protection via EssentialContract.nonReentrant (transient storage on chainid==1, storage otherwise)."
    },
